    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like there's no point in trying to bridge that gap. like i'm just wasting energy trying to connect to a world that i'm not even a part of. what's even the point of keeping this up if it's never gonna change?",
